msgid "house wizard"
msgstr "house wizard"

#: ../../H/house-wizard.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../H/house-wizard.rst:9
msgid ""
"[prob. : from ad-agency tradetalk, ‘house freak’] A hacker occupying a "
"technical-specialist, R&D, or systems position at a commercial shop. A "
"really effective house wizard can have influence out of all proportion to "
"his/her ostensible rank and still not have to wear a suit. Used esp. of Unix"
" wizards. The term house guru is equivalent."
msgstr ""
"[おそらく広告代理店の業界用語‘house "
"freak’より]商業的な職場で技術専門職、研究開発、またはシステムの地位を占めるハッカー。本当に有能なhouse "
"wizardは、その表向きの肩書に不釣り合いなほどの影響力を持ち、しかもスーツを着る必要もない。特にUnixウィザードについて使われる。house "
"guruという用語は等価である。"
